column1: Daily Weather Observations for Point Hicks, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3065.201603
Most observations taken from Point Hicks, pressure taken from Gabo Island.
Gabo Island is several kilometres to the east of Point Hicks, so pressures may vary markedly.
Temperature, humidity, wind, cloud and rainfall observations are from Point Hicks (Lighthouse) {station 084070}
Pressure observations are from Gabo Island Lighthouse {station 084016}
